    <section>
      <title>National Weather Service Offices</title>
      <para>
	Currently, none of the NWS DECs have E-Team capability.  As a
	consequence, NWS DECs will be notified by telephone as
	appropriate.
      </para>
    </section>
    <section>
      <title>Regional and Local Incidents</title>
      <para>
	In the case of a regional or local event where the SEC becomes
	involved before the DEC, the SEC will typically notify the
	affected DEC by telephone.  Depending on the incident, nearby
	DECs may also be notified.
      </para>
    </section>
